name: 凯蒂·何明
introduction: Overview (1)Height	 5' 2" (1.57 m)Mini Bio (1)Katie Hemming is an American actor and singer born and raised in Tacoma, WA. She has been performing since she was two years old in school plays, community theatre, operas, singing in multiple choirs including Tacoma Youth Chorus, and competing in classical vocal competitions. In January 2015, she made the decision to pursue acting as a career and has starred in numerous independent films and shorts such as "Marla Mae," "Call 2 Romance," and "#Kidnapped." Katie has a strong love of the craft and has trained in improv and Meisner as well as taking workshops in Method and Adler.
